title: Blood is the Harvest (Eclipse)
description:
'Blood is the Harvest', by Clint McElroy and Luciano Quieroz, is the next entry in the Eclipse Comics Upload Project.

Sooooooo. What can I tell you about this series? Well, it's four issues, in black and white, published by Eclipse in 1992 as part of their 'F/X' line. Also, it's about vampires.

That's all I got. Need to work on my salespitch, no?

REGARDLESS, this torrent has all four issues. Thanks be to the creative teams and the scanners! Get it, seed it!
